The area of the parallelogram formed by $\mathbf{0},$ $\mathbf{a},$ $\mathbf{b},$ and $\mathbf{a} + \mathbf{b}$ is
\[|(3)(2) - (-5)(1)| = 11,\]so the area of the triangle is $\boxed{\frac{11}{2}}.$

